03:09.965 --> 03:11.310
60 GRAND, MAN.

03:11.310 --> 03:12.827
I THINK I SAW, LIKE,
FOUR OR FIVE OF THESE AT SEMA.

03:12.827 --> 03:15.413
THEY ARE REALLY HOT RIGHT NOW,
BUT THEY'RE ALL LIFTED.

03:15.413 --> 03:16.862
THEY'RE ALL FOUR-WHEEL DRIVE.

03:16.862 --> 03:18.586
THEY PULL THE TOPS OFF,
GO DRIVE THEM ON THE BEACH,

03:18.586 --> 03:20.172
PUT LS MOTORS IN THEM.

03:20.172 --> 03:21.724
THAT'S REALLY WHAT'S
GOING ON RIGHT NOW.

03:21.724 --> 03:23.000
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
TO THIS?

03:23.000 --> 03:24.379
BECAUSE I DON'T KNOW IF I CAN
SELL IT TO YOU

03:24.379 --> 03:25.586
IF YOU'RE GONNA...
-I DON'T KNOW.

03:25.586 --> 03:27.034
I JUST GOT A COUPLE OF STUPID
IDEAS, BUT...

03:27.034 --> 03:28.275
DON'T LET HIM FOOL YOU.
HE'S GOT MORE THAN A COUPLE.

03:28.275 --> 03:31.275
YEAH. [ LAUGHS ]

03:31.275 --> 03:33.448
IF YOU MISSED THE 1970s
FOUR-WHEELING CRAZE,

03:33.448 --> 03:35.344
HERE'S THE DEAL WITH SCOUTS.
[ HORN HONKS ]

03:35.344 --> 03:38.517
THE FIRST SCOUTS WERE BUILT IN
1961 TO COMPETE WITH THE JEEP.

03:38.517 --> 03:41.103
THEY WERE ALSO SOLD
AS THE OUTDOORSMAN'S VEHICLE,

03:41.103 --> 03:42.586
BUT HAD A TOUCH
OF STYLE AND COMFORT

03:42.586 --> 03:46.724
THAT MADE THE SCOUT SORT
OF THE FORERUNNER OF THE S.U.V.

03:46.724 --> 03:48.448
THE SCOUT II DEBUTED IN '71,

03:48.448 --> 03:50.689
AND THE BASIC SHEET METAL
DIDN'T CHANGE MUCH RIGHT UP

03:50.689 --> 03:55.310
UNTIL THE LAST ONE
CAME OFF THE LINE IN 1980.

03:55.310 --> 03:56.344
LOOK AT THIS.

03:56.344 --> 03:57.793
YOU GOT SCOUTS
ALREADY IN THE YARD.

03:57.793 --> 04:00.206
YOU ARE A SCOUT AFICIONADO,
IT LOOKS LIKE.

04:00.206 --> 04:01.586
ENTHUSIAST.

04:01.586 --> 04:03.206
-I CAN'T GET OUT.
-"DUKES OF HAZZARD," MAN.

04:03.206 --> 04:05.379
COME ON.

04:05.379 --> 04:07.655
DOOR HANDLE DON'T WORK.
THAT'S A NEGATIVE.

04:07.655 --> 04:11.137
-GET OUT.
-ALL RIGHT.

04:11.137 --> 04:14.862
SO THIS IS, WHAT, A 304
OR A 345, SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

04:14.862 --> 04:16.551
I'M GUESSING IT'S THE 345.

04:16.551 --> 04:17.862
IT'S BASICALLY AN ORPHAN ENGINE.

04:17.862 --> 04:19.172
