AFTERMARKET PARTS

04:19.172 --> 04:21.827
FOR THESE THINGS,
SO IF YOU WANT TO HOP

04:21.827 --> 04:23.344
THIS THING UP,
YOU'RE KIND OF ON YOUR OWN.

04:23.344 --> 04:25.103
THIS IS A BOAT ANCHOR
RIGHT HERE.

04:25.103 --> 04:27.034
HONESTLY, YOU CAN'T LEAVE
THAT ENGINE IN IT.

04:27.034 --> 04:28.241
JUST TOSS IT, YEAH.

04:28.241 --> 04:29.413
THIS IS A PROBLEM.

04:29.413 --> 04:30.896
THE QUARTER PANEL
IS A LITTLE BENT, TOO.

04:30.896 --> 04:32.896
YOU CAN GET ALL THE PARTS
YOU NEED FOR THIS.

04:32.896 --> 04:34.034
THEY HAVE THEM.

04:34.034 --> 04:35.034
EVEN THOUGH THE ENGINE
HAS NO AFTERMARKET,

04:35.034 --> 04:36.517
REALLY, THE BODY PANELS DO.

04:36.517 --> 04:38.620
ONLY THING THEY DON'T HAVE
IS THE FRONT FENDERS.

04:38.620 --> 04:40.827
MAN, I DIDN'T THINK
HE CRAWLED UNDER THE...

04:40.827 --> 04:42.000
Richard:
IT'S GOT A COUPLE OF DENTS,

04:42.000 --> 04:43.793
BUT IT'S ONE OWNER,
VERY LITTLE RUST,

04:43.793 --> 04:46.137
SO IF I CAN GET
A GOOD SOLID TRUCK

04:46.137 --> 04:48.310
THAT'S NOT GONNA BE RUSTY
WHEN WE TAKE IT APART,

04:48.310 --> 04:49.758
THAT'S WHAT I'M LOOKING FOR.

04:49.758 --> 04:51.000
-I LOVE THE INTERIOR.
-YEAH.

04:51.000 --> 04:52.206
IF THIS THING HAS ONE THING
GOING FOR IT,

04:52.206 --> 04:53.724
IT'S THE CURB APPEAL,
THE ORANGE PAINT,

04:53.724 --> 04:55.724
THE STRIPES, THE PLAID SEATS.

04:55.724 --> 04:56.965
IT'S PRETTY COOL.

04:56.965 --> 04:58.965
I'M PRETTY GOOD AT POKER
AND READING PEOPLE AND,

04:58.965 --> 05:01.931
YOU KNOW, I THINK THEY GOT
HEARTS IN THEIR EYES, YOU KNOW?

05:01.931 --> 05:04.000
LITTLE EMOJI.

05:04.000 --> 05:06.586
ALL RIGHT. HOW MUCH IS IT?

05:06.586 --> 05:08.620
-$15,900.
-LIKE, $15,000?

05:08.620 --> 05:10.586
-$15,900.
-OH, MAN.

05:10.586 --> 05:12.034
MAN,
I AM IN THE WRONG BUSINESS.

05:12.034 --> 05:14.517
THEY'VE REALLY WENT UP, RICHARD.
THEY'RE STILL GOING UP.

05:14.517 --> 05:16.379
HOW ABOUT $10,000?

05:16.379 --> 05:19.620
