-YOU KNOW WHERE WE'RE AT.

05:19.620 --> 05:21.862
-I MEAN, $11,000?
-I WANT TO SEE IT DONE.

05:21.862 --> 05:24.137
I MEAN, I'D LIKE
TO SELL IT TO YOU.

05:24.137 --> 05:25.724
COME UP A LITTLE BIT AND...

05:25.724 --> 05:30.655
I JUST CAME UP TO $11,000.

05:30.655 --> 05:32.034
HOW ABOUT $12,500?

05:32.034 --> 05:33.586
ALL RIGHT, MAN, $12,500.

05:33.586 --> 05:34.689
-$12,500, HUH?
-IT'S A DEAL.

05:34.689 --> 05:36.620
-WE'LL DO IT. RIGHT ON.
-ALL RIGHT, COOL.

05:36.620 --> 05:38.068
CONGRATULATIONS.
YOU OWN A SCOUT.

05:38.068 --> 05:39.310
IT'LL BE THE FIRST ONE
I'VE EVER OWNED.

05:39.310 --> 05:42.310
-YOU GOT TO HAVE SOME MUSCLE.
-[ LAUGHS ]

05:42.310 --> 05:43.689
SO WE ENDED UP PAYING
$12,500 FOR IT,

05:43.689 --> 05:45.758
WHICH IS PROBABLY A LITTLE
MORE THAN I SHOULD HAVE,

05:45.758 --> 05:47.172
BUT IT'S THE TRUCK
I NEEDED AT THE TIME

05:47.172 --> 05:49.517
I NEEDED IT IN THE CITY
WHERE I LIVE.

05:49.517 --> 05:52.068
YEAH, LET'S GO IN THE HOUSE
AND DO A LITTLE PAPERWORK.

05:52.068 --> 05:53.310
