IN MY POCKET.

05:53.310 --> 05:54.586
Brian: I REALLY THINK THAT
IT'S GONNA BE HARD

05:54.586 --> 05:56.172
TO BREAK NEW GROUND WITH IT,

05:56.172 --> 05:58.413
