1979 INTERNATIONAL SCOUT.

06:26.724 --> 06:28.103
IT'S ORANGE.

06:28.103 --> 06:29.310
WELL, THAT'S THE ONE THING
THAT I DIG ABOUT IT.

06:29.310 --> 06:31.448
-I DIG THE ORANGE.
-ORANGE YOU GLAD IT WAS RUNNING?

06:31.448 --> 06:33.379
ORANGE YOU GLAD
I'M NOT GONNA PAINT IT BLACK?

06:33.379 --> 06:34.689
IT DIDN'T SOUND VERY GOOD.

06:34.689 --> 06:36.724
IT'S NOT HEALTHY AT ALL
