20:56.172 --> 20:58.310
AND GET THEM HERE SUPER FAST,

20:58.310 --> 21:00.275
THE FASTEST WE'VE EVER
GOTTEN THEM HERE,

21:00.275 --> 21:02.344
AND DOESN'T MATTER
BECAUSE THE ONE TIME

