21:34.379 --> 21:37.275
BECAUSE OF THAT CURVEBALL YOU
THREW US WHEN THE WHEELS

21:37.275 --> 21:39.655
THAT KIND OF CHANGED OUR IDEA
OF WHAT WE WERE BUILDING.

21:39.655 --> 21:41.827
REMEMBER THAT?

21:41.827 --> 21:43.206
THESE GUYS ARE TALKING
ABOUT CURVEBALLS

21:43.206 --> 21:45.103
AND HOW THINGS HAVE CHANGED.
NOTHING'S CHANGED.

21:45.103 --> 21:46.586
I LAID OUT MY VISION
FOR THE SCOUT,

21:46.586 --> 21:48.931
AND THEY GOT IT WRONG,
SO NOW THEY GOT TO FIX IT.

21:48.931 --> 21:50.241
HEY, RICHARD.

21:50.241 --> 21:51.482
WE COULD JUST BUILD BUILD
THE DRAG CAR. IT'S HERE.

21:51.482 --> 21:53.965
NO DRAG CAR.
