23:28.379 --> 23:29.758
TAKE A COUPLE OF THOSE THINGS
OFF YOUR WRIST.

23:29.758 --> 23:30.793
YOU'LL BE ABLE TO AFFORD IT.

23:30.793 --> 23:32.896
-12 SECONDS.
-No bid.

23:32.896 --> 23:36.310
CLOSING, HIGH BID $760,000.

23:36.310 --> 23:38.793
I thought that thing would stall
at about $550,000.

23:38.793 --> 23:40.689
That just means that we did
build a badass car,

23:40.689 --> 23:42.172
and it's going
for record pricing.

23:42.172 --> 23:44.413
I TOTALLY AGREE WITH RICHARD
THAT THAT WAS WAY TOO MUCH MONEY

23:44.413 --> 23:46.655
FOR HIM
TO WANT TO SPEND TO REBUY A CAR,

23:46.655 --> 23:51.413
BUT WHAT THIS DOES DO,
FOR $760,000, IS IT CEMENTS

23:51.413 --> 23:55.172
GAS MONKEY GARAGE'S PLACE
IN BUILDING HIGH-END CARS.

23:55.172 --> 23:57.413
YEP. OKAY. YOU HAVE A BEER.
I'M GOING TO HAVE A COFFEE.

23:57.413 --> 23:58.724
LATER.

23:58.724 --> 23:59.793
[ PHONE THUDS ]

