THIS THING UP.

25:27.896 --> 25:35.551
♪♪

25:35.551 --> 25:36.827
WHILE JOHN'S CUTTING OUT
THE FLOOR

25:36.827 --> 25:40.068
BEFORE DROPPING THE SCOUT
ONTO THE NEW CHASSIS,

25:40.068 --> 25:42.000
